I thought you were dead for sure.

147
00:14:34,773 --> 00:14:37,105
But that's not all
your own blood.

148
00:14:37,243 --> 00:14:38,938
Is it?

149
00:14:44,083 --> 00:14:46,711
It's okay. We can talk
about that later. Here.

150
00:14:49,288 --> 00:14:52,086
