clean up these wounds.

151
00:15:27,393 --> 00:15:29,020
Don't worry.

152
00:15:29,161 --> 00:15:31,254
I've done this before.

153
00:15:31,397 --> 00:15:34,366
Mostly to myself.

154
00:15:34,500 --> 00:15:37,765
Whiskey should help.
But I'm not gonna lie to you.

155
00:15:37,903 --> 00:15:39,427
