161
00:16:24,817 --> 00:16:27,877
Well, your modeling career
might be over,

162
00:16:28,020 --> 00:16:30,511
but you're gonna
heal up okay I think.

163
00:16:32,591 --> 00:16:34,889
Here.

164
00:16:37,663 --> 00:16:40,097
Don't worry. It's just water.

165
00:16:41,567 --> 00:16:43,330
