166
00:16:44,636 --> 00:16:46,570
Be my guest.

167
00:16:55,848 --> 00:16:58,180
We got something in common,
you and me.

168
00:17:00,019 --> 00:17:03,216
I'm not talkin' about the whiskey.

169
00:17:03,355 --> 00:17:05,915
Do you know what
I am talkin' about?

170
00:17:09,461 --> 00:17:11,452
