174
00:17:33,986 --> 00:17:36,113
I like the ones of that woman.

175
00:17:38,157 --> 00:17:40,887
Is she your mom?

176
00:17:50,269 --> 00:17:53,397
They've already
started lookin' for you.

177
00:17:53,539 --> 00:17:56,269
They'll be here soon.

178
00:17:56,408 --> 00:17:58,205
Now...

179
00:17:58,343 --> 00:18:01,506
as I see it,
you got three options.

180
00:18:01,647 --> 00:18:03,376
You can keep runnin'.

181
00:18:03,515 --> 00:18:06,484
If you do that, you'll either die out here
or they'll catch you.

182
00:18:06,618 --> 00:18:07,983
You can turn yourself in.

183
00:18:08,120 --> 00:18:10,987
If you do that,
they'll put you away for sure.

184
00:18:11,123 --> 00:18:15,355
