I can guarantee you that.

185
00:18:15,494 --> 00:18:17,485
Or you can stay with me.

186
00:18:19,565 --> 00:18:24,127
I can hide you
so they won't find you.

187
00:18:24,269 --> 00:18:27,761
They'll come and talk to me and
I'll tell 'em I don't know anything.

188
00:18:27,906 --> 00:18:30,670
Then they'll take me to town
and ask me again

189
00:18:30,809 --> 00:18:33,403
