on one action...

199
00:19:09,448 --> 00:19:12,849
rather than what's
in your heart.

200
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:18,515
I know what's
in your heart, Henry.

201
00:19:18,657 --> 00:19:20,181
I saw it out there.

202
00:19:22,895 --> 00:19:24,658
I see it in your eyes.

203
00:19:29,001 --> 00:19:32,664
You gotta decide right now.
They'll be on top of us soon.

204
00:19:36,775 --> 00:19:38,766
