205
00:19:53,525 --> 00:19:57,120
I'll bring you
food and water when I can.

206
00:19:57,262 --> 00:20:01,164
You can't ever step foot out of here
until I come and get you.

207
00:20:01,300 --> 00:20:03,063
Okay?

208
00:20:04,670 --> 00:20:07,730
Afterwards, no light at night.

209
00:20:07,873 --> 00:20:10,034
And no fires ever.

210
00:20:10,175 --> 00:20:12,234
The smoke will give away
your position.

211
00:20:12,377 --> 00:20:15,471
It'll get cold in here at night,

212
00:20:15,614 --> 00:20:17,514
but you're a tough kid.

213
00:20:17,649 --> 00:20:20,083
Right?

214
00:20:21,353 --> 00:20:23,821
You understand all that?

215
00:20:25,424 --> 00:20:26,857
It's gonna be okay.

216
00:20:28,126 --> 00:20:29,559
Trust me.

217
00:21:14,039 --> 00:21:15,472
Come in.

218
00:21:19,511 --> 00:21:21,206
Hey.

219
00:21:23,415 --> 00:21:25,406
How you doin', man?

220
00:21:28,253 --> 00:21:30,721
