221
00:21:30,856 --> 00:21:32,756
Your mom?

222
00:21:32,891 --> 00:21:35,257
She hasn't been talkin' much.

223
00:21:35,394 --> 00:21:38,727
She didn't say much to us either.

224
00:21:40,766 --> 00:21:43,860
